parameters:
??? : I am Aries, the priestess of the
current.

Aries: While I was walking in the holy
city of Logres, I happened to come
across you.

Aries: You were very weak, so I carried
you to my room. You slept for about ten
days, you know.
Zerachiel: Aries took care of me, huh.

Zerachiel: Thank you. I'm called
Zerachiel.
Aries: Nice to meet you, Zerachiel-sama.

Aries: So that's what happened... in the
Orpheus sect...

Zerachiel: I can't just silently turn
back after receiving such humiliation.

Aries: I can feel your emotions so
strongly that it hurts.

Aries: I will also assist you to the
best of my abilities.

Aries: Yes, I cannot forgive the
existence of the Orpheus sect.

Aries: Hehe, I have a question for you
instead.

Aries: Could it be that the mark on
Zerachiel-sama's stomach is the Lust
Mark...?

Aries: So it really is the Lust Mark,
isn't it?

Zerachiel: Ah, those guys! I absolutely
won't forgive them!

Aries: When an angel's Lust Mark is
engraved, it is a sign that they have
become impure due to feeling too much
pleasure.

Aries: While receiving cruel treatment
from the organization, I must have
fallen from grace.

Zerachiel: Will I always be like
this...?

Aries: The angel's Lust Mark is a sign
of their fall from grace... It cannot be
cured.

Aries: However, I don't think there's
any need to be so pessimistic.

Aries: Normally, those who have the Lust
Mark engraved on them become captivated
by pleasure immediately...

Aries: Even though the Lust Mark is
blossoming, Zerachiel-sama is still
maintaining her sense of self.

Aries: You don't seem to have any
outward sexual desires, and it seems
like you have resistance against the
Lust Mark.

Aries: If not for that, by now my mind
would have collapsed.

Aries: I believe that even if you harbor
the Lust Mark for a while, it won't
particularly progress in eroding you.

Zerachiel: If that's the case, then I
can breathe a sigh of relief...

Aries: While it is true that it arouses
those around her more and weakens her
resistance to sexual activities, there
are still drawbacks...

Zerachiel: Well, I guess there's no
helping it. I'll try to be careful too.

Aries: Let's think about how to
infiltrate the Orpheus Sect now.

Zerachiel: I would like to challenge
them head-on...

Zerachiel: It seems like my weapon was
taken away.

Aries: In that case, securing weapons is
the top priority, isn't it?

Aries: It seems like you've lost your
power, and in your current state, you
wouldn't even be able to defeat a slime.

Zerachiel: First, we need to earn money
in order to buy weapons.

Aries: Helping people in need, selling
fish from fishing, investigating
suspicious places...

Aries: I believe there are several ways
to obtain weapons.

Zerachiel: Let's walk around the town
right away and think about how to
procure weapons.

Aries: Once we're ready, let's
infiltrate the Orpheus Sect.

Aries: The Orpheus Sect is located to
the east of the town.
Aries: And also, I will give you this.

Aries: If you have any questions, they
are written there.
